CustomField.description: Digital Moms tend to be more tech-savvy and resourceful than their counterparts without children when it comes to online and mobile activities. Digital Moms identifies a household's likelihood to contain a Mom that is frequently online, and a frequent social networker. 1=Extremely Likely,2=Highly Likely,3=Very Likely,4=More than Likely,5=Likely,6=Somewhat Likely,7=Very Unlikely,8=Highly Unlikely,9=Extremely Unlikely,
